\": \"her behaviour\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'inappropriate atmosphere.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"false information\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not want to make any statement but I am not going to let lies affect me either,' Alonso added alongside a photo of her enjoying a drink as the sun set.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any statement\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"lies\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"a drink\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun set\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read More:Olympic swimmer Luana Alonso removed from Athletes' Village over claims she created an 'inappropriate environment' Read More:Shock as Olympic swimmer, 21, suffers asthma attack and collapses after race as she is carried off on stretcher The 20-year-old Paraguayan, who failed to qualify from the heats of the 100m butterfly,had been seen walking round in her own choice of outfits rather than the official uniforms provided by team chiefs and visiting luxury Parisian hotels and restaurants before posting the photos to her 600,000 social media followers .\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.8124999943799553, \"rank\": 0.23076923076919917, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\":